value.0: ACN Deposit Boxes.  Deposit your items into the deposit box.  There are 40 of them.  Only need to use one at a time.  They will remain safe for ten minutes after you last dropped an item into a box.  Boxes will be tagged by your CDKey to secure your items.  The lock will again unlock after ten minutes.  You will know if the deposit box is in use cause it will have VFX_DUR_BIGBYS_GRASPING_HAND visual effect.  The effect will remain for ten minutes or until the items are received.
READ ME BEFORE ENTERING THE DEPOSIT BOX ROOM!
